but otherwise normal.

16:43.635 --> 16:46.102
I just reinstalled this app on my phone.

16:46.104 --> 16:48.303
Please don't make me regret it.

16:48.305 --> 16:51.507
Hello, women of the Internet.

16:51.509 --> 16:52.541
I'm Gary.

16:52.543 --> 16:55.878
I like long walks on the beach,

16:55.880 --> 16:57.546
